divs: Sighting DetailsI live in Hungary (Europe). I was on the terrace (about 11 AM) when I noticed this slowly flying, noiseless, dark brown disk shaped object. I caught my mobile phone (Samsung SGH-E250) and I did a photo from the object. The diameter of the object was approximately 30-40 feet. The picture was taken on Kaposvar, Hungary. Tibor
trends: There have been no other sightings in Kaposvár
This sighting has never been favorited.
